Package com.revature.GSQL.Annotations

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Column
    Annotation to declare a matching column inside a table.
    Getter
    Annotation to declare a getter for a value that is also stored inside a table.
    PrimaryKey
    Annotation to indicate that a field is the primary key.
    SerialKey
    Annotation to declare a field as being a serial key inside of a table.
    Setter
    Annotation to declare a Setter for a value stored inside of a table.
    Table
    Annotation to declare an object represents a table inside of a database.
